historischen Entwicklung.  aIn 1982 the movie Blade Runner depicted a dystopia of the urban image of Los Angeles - yet the scenario of terror did not come true. Christiane Feuerstein describes innovative concepts of the local urban development.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 4aArchitektur. 4aBlade Runner. 4aFilm. 4aGentrifizierung. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aMedien. 4aSoziologie. 4aStadt. 4aStadterneuerung. 4aStadtforschung. 4aStadtgeschichte. 4aStadtplanung. 4aTurnaround Urbanism. 4aUrban Studies. 4aUrbanität. 4aWohnen. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / Urban.2bisacsh  aArchitecture.  aBlade Runner.  aCity.  aCultural Studies.  aFilm.  aGentrification.  aHabitation.  aMedia.  aSociology.  aTurnaround Urbanism.  aUrban History.  aUrban Planning.  aUrban Renewal.  aUrban Studies.  aUrbanity.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2019 Part 2z978311076669108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2019z9783110606485oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839443941zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839443941423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839443941/original  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-076669-1  DG Plus PP Package 2019 Part 2b2019  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DSWb2019